full_address: 1043 Pimpama Jacobs Well Road, Jacobs Well, Qld 4208
description:
Welcome to 1043 Pimpama Jacobs Well Road, Jacobs Well. Here is the perfect opportunity for your own episode of the Block, located in the heart of Jacobs Well. Sitting on an impressive 612sqm and backing onto the old turf farm, this 3 bedroom home is waiting for you to claim ownership.

Featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 with built-ins, 1 bathroom and single car lock up, this property is definitely one to see. Being a blank canvas this gives you the opportunity to either move in and sit on it for a bit, renovate what is there or demolish and start fresh. Kitchen and bathroom have had an upgrade from their original condition. Outside you have a lard shed that has been turned into a rumpus room plus 2 other sheds on the property so plenty of extra storage.

Features Include
• 3 bedrooms 1 with built-ins
• 1 bathroom
• Updated kitchen
• Updated bathroom with separate bath and shower
• Laundry
• Linen Cupboard
• Electric cooktop
• 3x sheds
• 3x water tanks
• 1x reverse cycle air conditioning to dining room

Jacobs Well has a very laid back lifestyle with a great community atmosphere. Living in the Jacobs Well community you can spend your weekends out on the boat fishing & crabbing or fishing off the Jetty. Take the Jet Ski out for a trip over to South Stradbroke, Tipplers or Couran Cove.
You are only 15 minutes to major shopping centres, train stations, M1, theme parks and 40 minutes to some of Queensland's best beaches.

Give me a call today to inspect on 0437 112 311

For all of your home loan needs, please contact our friendly broker, Conrad Palmer on 0410 296 050.

All inspections will be conducted adhering to COVID-19 Social Distancing Guidelines and Ray White's no-contact policy.
